    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped lemongrass</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to the pan and cook 1 min</p><p>Add the<strong> coconut stock</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 6-7 min or until the mushrooms have softened</p>",
