      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> pulled meat-free chick'n</strong> to the pan with the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lime</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min further or until the meat-free chick'n is warmed through – this is your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>chick'n tom kha soup</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
