      "instruction": "<p>Discard the<strong> outer lemongrass layers</strong> from the <strong>basmati rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>meat-free chick'n tom kha soup</strong> in bowls with the<strong> basmati rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
